# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:16
translate spanish jamies1_bb8e4698:

    # gnd "I guess I mostly just watch TV."
    gnd "Supongo que sobre todo veo la tele."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:18
translate spanish jamies1_852cc3d1:

    # gnd "I study a lot for school, but sometimes my brain gets so fried that I need to give it a break."
    gnd "Estudio mucho para la universidad, pero a veces mi cerebro se fríe tanto que necesito darle un respiro."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:19
translate spanish jamies1_b9329686:

    # gnd "So I'll just sit in front of the TV and binge for hours."
    gnd "Así que me siento delante de la tele y me paso horas viendo series."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:21
translate spanish jamies1_03442701:

    # gnd "I do a lot of housework too though. Cooking meals for Daddy, cleaning up the house, paying all the bills."
    gnd "Aunque también hago muchas tareas domésticas. Cocinar para papá, limpiar la casa, pagar todas las facturas."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:22
translate spanish jamies1_13e4bb16:

    # pc "You pay the bills?"
    pc "¿Tú pagas las facturas?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:24
translate spanish jamies1_84cf7c79:

    # gnd "Well, it's Daddy's money, but yeah, I make sure everything gets paid. He's never been too good with the finances. Mom always did that."
    gnd "Bueno, es el dinero de papá, pero sí, me aseguro de que todo se pague. Él nunca se le han dado muy bien las finanzas. Mamá siempre se encargaba de eso."

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:26
translate spanish jamies1_9a57bf03:

    # gnd "I try to do as much as I can to help him out, you know?"
    gnd "Intento hacer todo lo que puedo para ayudarle, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Jamie/JamieConversation/jamies1.rpy:27
